            <title>网民售卖快餐店绝版塑胶餐具，标价 HK$3,000 不议价送纸巾</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/netizen-sell-disposable-spoon-3000-hkd/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=netizen-sell-disposable-spoon-3000-hkd</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/netizen-sell-disposable-spoon-3000-hkd/life-tech/green-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:00:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[环保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[走塑]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1230870</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日（22 日）正式实施首阶段即弃胶餐具和塑胶产品管制，部分连锁快餐店因应法例停止供应即弃塑胶餐具，有「独具慧眼」的网民看见商机，在知名网上买卖平台出售本地一间连锁快餐店的橙色即弃餐具，表示该套餐具非常经典，且已经绝版。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-1-694x537.png" alt="" width="694" height="537" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-1-694x537.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-1.png 1163w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：Carousell</p><p>由图片可见，网民标价 3,000 元出售快餐店即弃餐具，更指这套餐具非常经典，而且已经绝版。售卖餐具的网民更表示：「不议价送原装纸巾」。</p><p>另外亦有幽默的网民在该网站刊登相近的广告，并风趣的表示「肚饿食面用咗只叉，半价卖出」。该名网民又指，这套外卖餐具套装「极具收藏价值，更可多次清洗循环使用，可谓环保人士恩物 」</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-584x580.png" alt="" width="584" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-584x580.png 584w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-906x900.png 906w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-144x144.png 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2.png 1153w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 584px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：Carousell</p><p>知名网络讨论区「LIHKG」上有网民表示，以前储存一大堆即弃餐具，但已经全数丢弃，对此感到可惜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/33-694x188.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="188" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/33-694x188.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/33.jpg 877w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3680599/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.carousell.com.hk/p/%E7%B5%95%E7%89%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%AB%E6%B4%BB%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E6%A9%99%E8%86%A0%E9%A4%90%E5%85%B7%E5%A5%97%E8%A3%9D%EF%BC%88%E8%82%9A%E9%A4%93%E9%A3%9F%E9%BA%B5%E7%94%A8%E5%92%97%E9%9A%BB%E5%8F%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%8A%E5%83%B9%E5%B9%B3%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%89-1299533959/?t-id=fSGOWyv1Ey_1713859673281&amp;t-referrer_browse_type=search_results&amp;t-referrer_page_type=search&amp;t-referrer_request_id=D8K3s-76rIw0Jppt&amp;t-referrer_search_query=%E7%B5%95%E7%89%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%BF%AB%E6%B4%BB&amp;t-referrer_search_query_source=direct_search&amp;t-referrer_sort_by=popular&amp;t-tap_index=2">Carousell</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3680599/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/22/paper-straw-pfas/life-tech/health/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">比利时大学：「走塑」纸饮管也可致癌 + 不育，研究指有不可降解 PFAS</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/netizen-sell-disposable-spoon-3000-hkd/life-tech/green-2/">网民售卖快餐店绝版塑胶餐具，标价 HK$3,000 不议价送纸巾</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
